heir investment progress with comprehensive analytics understand what works in your marketing campaign and what doesnt as you monitor investment activity from your dashboard in real time investor communications answer questions in a forumstyle comments section that creates transparency in your offering get notified instantly when investors request an introduction we also provide the email address of any registered user who has engaged with your offering page so you can convert them into shareholders streamlined deal execution investor verification if accredited investors participate in your offering our broker dealer will verify that they meet sec requirements our broker dealer also conducts customer identification program cip and antimoney laundering aml procedures to monitor proper handling of your funds regulatory compliance our broker dealer or funding portal will file your sec forms blue sky forms andor articles of incorporation on your behalf and assist with all the other legal documents necessary to close your round in a compliant manner ongoing postfundraising investor management flashfunders shareholder services we support you after the deal is done flashfunders shareholder services llc is an secregistered transfer agent that electronically records all your investors shares in bookentry format should you elect to utilize their services we maintain an organized record of your cap table manage all inbound investor requests and help disseminate your annual financial reports learn more frequently asked questions what types of companies raise capital on flashfunders weve democratized access to all investors and we welcome businesses from all sectors most companies on our platform are looking to raise between  and  million but that can vary widely beyond our outlined read more what are the requirements to raise capital on flashfunders your company must be forprofit with a tax id number ein you must be over  a us resident with a social security number a us address