t sustainable transportation network this effort is driven by a community of individuals who are passionate about creating a better way to travel over the last few years unprecedented advances have been achieved in vehicle technology due to the advent of an electric car platform the along with new driver assistance features and general design improvements travel by car can now be vastly safer more comfortable and more economical than ever before our mission tesloop is to enable our community of travelers to create an amazing travel experience on a sustainable transportation platform offered in a cloud services model here’s how it works passenger membership   passengers can book seats in shared cars along tesloop’s scheduled citytocity routes just like you would on an airline for less than the price of gas passengers are driven in safe  sustainable vehicles with friendly service and healthy  satisfying amenities current routes include la  las vegas oc  las vegas and soon palm springs routes in the near future will include la  san diego la  santa barbara la  mt view san mateo  reno and more passenger membership is currently targeted at those who travel between southern california and las vegas or palm springs at least  times a year and is offered at a discounted price of month for the first year regular price is  per route or network wide for   current travel rates between cities is    cents per mile la  las vegas  la  palm springs  la  santa barbara  la  mt view  pilot club membership   members who are interested in driving the tesloop experience can apply to join the pilots club after a standard online background check that verifies driving record and insurability pilot candidates can enroll in a short and free certification process the tesloop pilot’s certification provides training on vehicle operations proper use of the autopilot features and general tesloop procedures that promote the amazing travel experience once certified pilots are eligible to travel at no cost on all tesloop scheduled routes in the drivers seat  pilots can also book passage for their friends  family discount rates  by driving and booking they earn credits towards use of the tesla fleet for personal travel  for example a pilot driving two round trips between la and vegas over a month and booking two friends would receive  days of personal tesla usage tesloop is seeking founding pilots who are enthusiastic about promoting sustainable travel by educating others and enabling an amazing experience for all passengers currently the pilots club is by invitation only however those interested may sign up to receive an application when the program opens to the public founding team rahul sonnad president  cofounder linkedin rahul has been active in technology and startups since the ’s he founded his first startup theplatform in  which offered an industrialstrength online video management system this became the backend for services by verizon microsoft hulu qualcomm as well as comcast who acquired the company in  for over m rahul’s founded his next venture geodelic in  and offered a location based content expand bio rahul has been active in technology and startups since the ’s he founded his first startup theplatform in  which offered an industrialstrength online video management system this became the backend for services by verizon microsoft hulu qualcomm as well as comcast who acquired the company in  for over m rahul’s founded his next venture geodelic in  and offered a location based content discovery and mobile commerce service that was adopted by verizon universal studios theme parks and korea telecom before startups rahul worked as an engineering manager at adobe and at microsoft first as a product designer for ms word and later as the rd manager for all the asian versions of ms office a b suite of products he attended the harvard business school’s mba program received a masters in computer science with a  gpa and japanese from the university of washington